
INVERSE(2)                 silmul_efun                INVERSE(2)

名称
     inverse - 将萤幕反白

语法
     string inverse (string str);

描述
     If  this_player()  has  the  "vt100"  attribute  set,   this
     simul_efun  will  return  str  with  the "inverse on" escape
     sequence  added  in  front  and  the  "inverse  off"  escape
     sequence added to the end, so that the string will print out
     in inverse mode on a VT100-compatible terminal.

     注意:  Do NOT use ed to edit the file vt100.c, or the escape
     sequences  will be corrupted.  (ed strips out escape charac-
     ters).

相关命令
     blink, bold, underscore, clear_screen, clear_line,  up_line,
     erase_line

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/19/93
     wade@future 4/8/1996 翻译

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

